body:
@vksbhandary I'm using @aluo-x whl file and it's working.
Missing support of AVX2 instruction set in MSCV2015 and some compiling error made me install MSCV2017 based on discussion [10199](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/10199) but I ran into this issue. Thanks for suggestion, I will try to re-install and build again with VS2017 15.4 toolset.
